## Auth Flow

JWT RS256 — access token: 1h, refresh token: opaque stored in Redis (`refresh:{userId}` TTL 24h).

```java
// auth/AuthFilter.java  (jakarta.servlet.Filter, mapped to /api/* in web.xml)
String h = req.getHeader("Authorization");
if (h == null || !h.startsWith("Bearer ")) { send401(res); return; }
DecodedJWT jwt = jwtService.verify(h.substring(7));  // throws on bad/expired
req.setAttribute("userId", Long.valueOf(jwt.getSubject()));
chain.doFilter(req, res);
```

