## Kafka Topics

| Topic                | Key       | Consumers                                          |
|----------------------|-----------|----------------------------------------------------|
| `chat.messages`      | `chat_id` | persist, inbox-update, notify, ai                  |
| `chat.notifications` | —         | push consumer (device_tokens → FCM/APNs)           |
| `chat.ai.requests`   | —         | AiProvider call                                    |
| `chat.ai.responses`  | —         | Stored as normal message, fanned out               |
| `chat.analytics`     | —         | Metrics sink                                       |

