- [ ] Bootstrap `ServletContextListener` — open Hikari pool, Cassandra session, Redis client, Kafka producer; register Redis `chat-events` subscriber
- [ ] `JwtService` (RS256) + `AuthFilter` + signup/login/refresh servlets, bcrypt password hashing
- [ ] `WsHandshakeAuth` configurator — validate `?token=` before `onOpen`
- [ ] `LocalSessionRegistry` + `FanoutService` (Redis Pub/Sub) — cross-instance delivery
- [ ] `MessageService.handleSend` — dedup (LWT) → TimeUUID id → ACK → fan-out → Kafka
- [ ] `ConversationsServlet` (chat list) + `MessageHistoryServlet` (cursor paging by message_id)
- [ ] DTOs mirroring the frontend `mockData` shapes (one contract, both sides)

### P1 — Core chat features

- [ ] Read receipts + unread: `read_state` writes, Redis `unread:{user}:{chat}` counters
